1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:10,000
字幕转制｜天外生物
感谢原字幕制作者

2
00:00:38,830 --> 00:00:40,660
这是我迄今走过的岁月
Here's my day so far:

3
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:43,500
进过监狱 失去了我的梦中情人
Went to jail, lost the girl of my dreams,

4
00:00:43,670 --> 00:00:45,970
被别人打得屁滚尿流
and got my butt kicked pretty good.

5
00:00:46,610 --> 00:00:49,670
不过 更糟的事还在后头
Still, things could be a lot worse.

6
00:00:51,040 --> 00:00:52,410
噢 没错
Oh, that's right.

7
00:00:53,010 --> 00:00:54,810
我快要掉下去摔死了
I'm falling to my death.

8
00:00:55,450 --> 00:00:56,850
估计没更糟的了
Guess they can't.

9
00:00:57,580 --> 00:00:59,280
你要问 怎么会成这样？
How'd it all come to this, you ask?

10
00:01:00,650 --> 00:01:02,350
我的结局开始就已注定
My end starts at the beginning.

11
00:01:03,120 --> 00:01:04,520
最初的开始
The very beginning.

12
00:01:08,190 --> 00:01:10,060
没错 这就是我
Yes, that's me.

13
00:01:10,830 --> 00:01:13,530
我童年相当正常
I had a fairly standard childhood.

14
00:01:14,630 --> 00:01:17,540
我来自 你们可能会叫做 一个破碎的家庭
I came from, what you might call, a broken home.

15
00:01:18,940 --> 00:01:20,460
确实很破碎
Literally broken.

16
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:24,010
我都八天大了 还跟父母住在一起
I was eight days old and still living with my parents.

17
00:01:24,780 --> 00:01:26,370
多悲哀啊？
How sad is that?

18
00:01:26,980 --> 00:01:28,640
显然 生活该向前了
Clearly it was time to move on.

19
00:01:28,810 --> 00:01:31,580
这是你的仆人 他会照顾你的
Here is your Minion. He will take care of you.

20
00:01:31,780 --> 00:01:33,180
给你宾奇奶嘴
And here is your Binky.

21
00:01:34,220 --> 00:01:36,120
你命中注定成为…
You are destined for...

22
00:01:36,820 --> 00:01:40,520
我没听到最后那部分 不过似乎很重要
I didn't quite hear that last part, but it sounded important.

23
00:01:40,690 --> 00:01:43,320
- 命中注定成为…  - 什么？
- Destined for...  - What?

24
00:01:45,130 --> 00:01:47,830
我登上行程 去寻找自己的命运
I set out to find my destiny.

25
00:01:49,470 --> 00:01:53,700
结果 一个Glaupunkt信号区的孩子和我的想法如出一辙
Turns out a kid from the Glaupunkt quadrant had the exact same idea.

26
00:02:00,980 --> 00:02:04,110
就是那天 我见到了假正经先生…
That was the day I met Mr. Goody Two-Shoes...

27
00:02:06,650 --> 00:02:11,490
我们宏伟的较量从此开始
and our glorious rivalry was born.

28
00:02:16,060 --> 00:02:18,430
这将是我的命运吗？
Could this be what I was destined for?

29
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:21,060
奢华 梦幻的生活
A dream life filled with luxury.

30
00:02:23,070 --> 00:02:24,370
显然不是
Apparently not.

31
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:27,810
就连命运也有自己的喜好
Even fate picks its favorites.

32
00:02:29,180 --> 00:02:30,440
没什么大不了
No big deal.

33
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:33,270
一个截然不同的命运等待着我
A much different fate awaited me.

34
00:02:35,100 --> 00:02:37,400
[欢迎来到犯罪天才的大都会市监狱]

35
00:02:41,790 --> 00:02:44,690
一个婴儿！好贴心啊
A baby! How thoughtful.

36
00:02:44,860 --> 00:02:47,620
噢 对 对啊 我看到它 就想到了你
Oh, yes. Yes, I saw it and thought of you.

37
00:02:48,630 --> 00:02:51,560
幸运地是 我找到了一个可爱的小地方来当家
Luckily I found a lovely little place to call home.

38
00:02:51,730 --> 00:02:52,890
我们可以养它吗？
Can we keep it?

39
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:56,630
这个地方教会了我对…
A place that taught me the differences between right...

40
00:02:57,940 --> 00:02:59,130
与错
and wrong.

41
00:02:59,610 --> 00:03:01,630
而另一边 假正经先生
Mr. Goody Two-Shoes, on the other hand,

42
00:03:01,810 --> 00:03:04,300
不费吹灰之力就过上了好日子
had life handed to him on a silver platter.

43
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:05,940
我们的宝贝会飞啊
Our baby can fly.

44
00:03:06,110 --> 00:03:08,340
是啊 是啊 对你来说最棒了 亲爱的
Yes, yes, nothing but the best for you, darling.

45
00:03:08,550 --> 00:03:12,780
翱翔之力 刀枪不入 发型超棒
The power of flight, invulnerability, and great hair.

46
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:17,120
但是我有厉害许多的地方
But I had something far, far greater.

47
00:03:17,660 --> 00:03:19,590
我智慧惊人…
My amazing intellect...

48
00:03:19,760 --> 00:03:22,280
还有创造破坏工具的本领超棒
and knack for building objects of mayhem.

49
00:03:28,870 --> 00:03:32,070
过了几年 因为表现良好
After a few years, and with some time off for good behavior,

50
00:03:32,470 --> 00:03:36,100
我得到机会进行学习 自我改善…
I was given an opportunity to better myself through learning...

51
00:03:36,880 --> 00:03:39,500
还是在一个陌生的地方 叫什么校
at a strange place called Shool.

52
00:03:40,780 --> 00:03:44,270
天才儿童学校 “专为天才儿童打造” 在那儿 我再次遇上了假正经先生
It was there that I once again ran into Mr. Goody Two-Shoes.

53
00:03:44,620 --> 00:03:48,280
他那时已经有了一大批没大脑的粉丝
He had already amassed a gigantic army of soft-headed groupies.

54
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:56,750
他就靠着大秀演技 还有挥霍精美小礼品
He bought their affections with showmanship

55
00:03:56,900 --> 00:03:59,260
来赚取他们的喜爱
and extravagant gifts of deliciousness.

56
00:04:01,730 --> 00:04:06,260
所以我也要做出爆玉米花 把那些没大脑的白痴给争取过来
So I, too, will make this popp-ed corn and win over those mindless drones.

57
00:04:06,410 --> 00:04:07,800
熄灯
Lights out.

58
00:04:25,590 --> 00:04:27,890
就是那时 我学到了一个艰难的道理:
That's when I learned a very hard lesson:

59
00:04:28,060 --> 00:04:30,720
好人获得所有的表扬和奉承
Good receives all the praise and adulation,

60
00:04:30,900 --> 00:04:33,760
而坏人只能在角落面壁思过
while evil is sent to quiet-time in the corner.

61
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:38,200
所以能否融入群体 真不是我能左右的
So fitting in wasn't really an option.

62
00:04:39,170 --> 00:04:41,640
当他们学习儿歌“海绵泡沫纸板书”的时候…
While they were learning the Ltsy Bitsy Spider...

63
00:04:42,610 --> 00:04:46,810
我在学习如何随心所欲地让活化物体脱水 再水化
I learned how to dehydrate animate objects and rehydrate them at will.

64
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:52,780
有段时间 就好像只有我和我的仆人与世界为敌
Some days, it felt like it was just me and Minion against the world.

65
00:04:54,250 --> 00:04:55,910
不管我多么努力
No matter how hard I tried,

66
00:04:56,090 --> 00:04:58,150
我总是个局外人
I was always the odd man out,

67
00:04:58,320 --> 00:05:00,090
被抛弃的人
the last one picked,

68
00:05:00,260 --> 00:05:02,350
出乱子的人 害群之马…
the screw-up, the black sheep...

69
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,890
砸他！
Get him!

70
00:05:04,060 --> 00:05:05,330
坏小孩
The bad boy.

71
00:05:10,270 --> 00:05:11,430
怪人！
Weirdo!

72
00:05:17,140 --> 00:05:18,970
这就是我的命运了？
Was this my destiny?

73
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:21,870
等下 可能就是
Wait, maybe it was.

74
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:25,850
我唯一擅长的就是做坏事
Being bad is the one thing I'm good at.

75
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:30,120
然后我恍然大悟: 如果我是个坏小孩
Then it hit me: If I was the bad boy,

76
00:05:30,290 --> 00:05:34,280
那我就要做所有人中最坏的那个
then I was going to be the baddest boy of them all.

77
00:05:36,130 --> 00:05:38,620
我命中注定成为超级大坏蛋
I was destined to be a super-villain,

78
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:41,430
我们注定要成为对头
and we were destined to be rivals.

79
00:05:42,670 --> 00:05:44,530
既知难逃一死
The die had been cast,

80
00:05:44,670 --> 00:05:48,900
那就开始好好经营我永恒 壮丽的终生事业吧
and so began an enduring, epic, lifelong career.

81
00:05:49,070 --> 00:05:51,100
我爱它
And I loved it.

82
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:55,410
我们之间的战争愈演愈烈
Our battles quickly got more elaborate.

83
00:05:56,150 --> 00:05:57,580
他赢了很多次
He would win some.

84
00:05:58,380 --> 00:06:00,220
我很多时候也险些获胜
I would almost win others.

85
00:06:00,750 --> 00:06:05,690
他取名为大都会侠 意为大都会市的保护者
He took the name Metro Man, defender of Metrocity.

86
00:06:05,990 --> 00:06:09,480
我决定要取个谦虚点的名号: 超级大坏蛋…
I decided to pick something a little more humble: Megamind...

87
00:06:10,030 --> 00:06:14,430
不可思议的帅气犯罪天才 精通所有的坏事
incredibly handsome criminal genius and master of all villainy.

88
00:06:15,100 --> 00:06:20,100
超级大坏蛋

89
00:06:25,950 --> 00:06:28,040
下班时间再看吧 开门
Read on your own time. Open up.

90
00:06:35,020 --> 00:06:36,490
- 嘿！ - 嘣！
- Hey!  - Boo!

91
00:06:40,490 --> 00:06:41,820
噢 早上好啊 监狱长
Oh, good morning, Warden.

92
00:06:41,990 --> 00:06:44,930
超级大新闻: 我已经改过自新啦 而且…
Great news: I'm a changed man, and...

93
00:06:45,100 --> 00:06:48,830
我已经准备好重新踏入社会 当个好市民了
and I'm ready to re-enter society as a solid citizen.

94
00:06:49,170 --> 00:06:51,400
你是个大坏蛋 而且永远都是大坏蛋
You're a villain, and you'll always be a villain.

95
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:54,230
你永远不会改过自新 而且永远也不能离开这儿
You'll never change, and you'll never leave.

96
00:06:54,410 --> 00:06:55,700
你真好玩
You're fun.

97
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:57,140
有人给你寄来个礼物
You got a present in the mail.

98
00:06:57,310 --> 00:06:58,670
是小狗吗？
Is it a puppy?

99
00:06:58,840 --> 00:07:04,010
大都会侠寄的 “让你算清八十五个无期徒刑的每一秒”
From Metro Man. "To count every second of your 85 life sentences."

100
00:07:04,180 --> 00:07:07,450
很奇怪啊 没想到大都会侠也会沾沾自喜
That's funny. Never thought Metro Man was the gloating type.

101
00:07:07,590 --> 00:07:10,320
噢 不过他品味确实不错 我就留下吧
Oh, but he does have nice taste. I think I'll keep it.

102
00:07:10,490 --> 00:07:12,620
你可以告诉我现在几点了吗？
Any chance you could give me the time?

103
00:07:12,760 --> 00:07:15,730
我可不想在大都会侠博物馆开幕式上迟到
I don't want to be late for the opening of the Metro Man Museum.

104
00:07:16,660 --> 00:07:19,430
啊 不好 看样子你必定要错过它
Oh no. Looks like you're gonna miss it,

105
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:21,500
迟到个几千年了
by several thousand years.

106
00:07:22,940 --> 00:07:24,030
噢 是吗？
Oh, am I?

107
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:32,070
大都会市市民们 大都会侠日快乐
Happy Metro Man Day, Metro City.

108
00:07:34,580 --> 00:07:37,110
今天天气很好 我们在美丽的市中心
It's a beautiful day in beautiful downtown,

109
00:07:37,280 --> 00:07:41,380
在此授予一位杰出人士 大都会侠以荣誉
where we're here to honor a beautiful man, Metro Man.

110
00:07:41,950 --> 00:07:46,120
他的心海纳百川 包罗万象
His heart is an ocean that's inside a bigger ocean.

111
00:07:46,790 --> 00:07:49,590
这么多年来 他以自己超凡的视觉注视着我们
For years he's been watching us with his super-vision,

112
00:07:49,760 --> 00:07:54,290
以超凡的力量拯救着我们 以超凡的心关爱着我们
saving us with his super-strength and caring for us with his super-heart.

113
00:07:54,670 --> 00:07:57,260
现在该我们给他些回报了
Now it's our turn to give something back.

114
00:07:57,440 --> 00:07:59,370
来自罗珊・罗奇 在大都会侠博物馆
This is Roxanne Ritchi, reporting live

115
00:07:59,540 --> 00:08:01,970
落成典礼发回的现场报道
from the dedication of the Metro Man Museum.

116
00:08:02,780 --> 00:08:04,770
哇 好了 现场直播让你说这种东西
Wow. OK, the stuff they make you read on-air,

117
00:08:04,940 --> 00:08:07,210
真是让人太难以置信了 简直疯了
that's un-freaking-believable. It's crazy.

118
00:08:07,380 --> 00:08:09,610
是我自己写的稿子 哈尔
I wrote that piece myself, Hal.

119
00:08:09,780 --> 00:08:11,180
我其实是想说
What I was trying to say was,

120
00:08:11,350 --> 00:08:14,050
我很难相信在现代社会中
I can't believe that in our modern society,

121
00:08:14,220 --> 00:08:16,710
他们会让这种真正的艺术出现在新闻里
they let, like, actual art get onto the news.

122
00:08:16,890 --> 00:08:18,190
- 真会圆场啊 哈尔  - 我们要不…
- Nice save, Hal.  - What are we...

123
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:20,450
去喝杯咖啡什么的吧
Like, let's just get a coffee or something.

124
00:08:20,630 --> 00:08:23,290
拜托 该好好去体验下大都会侠日了
Come on, it's time to get in the Metro Man Day spirit.

125
00:08:23,460 --> 00:08:24,860
好吧 如果我是大都会侠
Well, if I were Metro Man,

126
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,860
超级大坏蛋就不能老是绑架你成功了
Megamind wouldn't be kidnapping you all the time.

127
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:29,370
- 这是其一  - 嘴真甜 哈尔
- That's the first thing.  - That's sweet, Hal.

128
00:08:29,540 --> 00:08:32,830
我一定会好好看着你 就像澳洲野狗看护小孩子一样
And I'd be watching you, like a dingo watches a human baby.

129
00:08:33,040 --> 00:08:34,270
好吧 听起来…
OK, that sounded...

130
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:36,700
- 好吧 听起来有点奇怪  - 是有点 嗯
- OK, that sounded a little weird.  - A little bit. Yeah.

131
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:39,070
你现在这个奇怪的表情 让我感觉也怪怪的了
And you're making a weird face, and that's making me feel weird.

132
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,640
重点是 我会好好看着你 就像…
The point is, I would watch you like someone...

133
00:08:42,280 --> 00:08:45,110
不是爱人 我们没在恋爱 我不是说我爱你
Not love. We're not in love. I'm not saying I love you.

134
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:46,510
嘿 我爱你 管它的
Hey, I love you. Whatever.

135
00:08:46,690 --> 00:08:48,620
但是我不是说我爱上了你 我是说…
But I'm not saying like I'm in love with you. I'm saying...

136
00:08:49,390 --> 00:08:51,750
罗珊？Roxaroo？人呢
Roxanne? Roxaroo?

137
00:09:05,540 --> 00:09:06,830
- 哇… 怎么回事？ - 嘿…
- Whoa... What?  - Hey...

138
00:09:07,010 --> 00:09:10,000
回去工作 市民花钱不是让你们来玩的
Get back to work. The city doesn't pay you to loaf.

139
00:09:10,410 --> 00:09:12,170
- 站住！ - 喔 你们要干嘛 伙计？
- Freeze!  - Whoa. What are you doing, guys?

140
00:09:12,340 --> 00:09:14,140
是我啊！监狱长啊
It's me! It's the warden.

141
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:16,310
嘿！开门！
Hey! Open up!

142
00:09:23,660 --> 00:09:26,020
不 你们这些笨蛋 他骗了我们
No, you fools. He's tricked us.

143
00:09:26,490 --> 00:09:27,620
说对了
You were right.

144
00:09:29,460 --> 00:09:31,020
我永远会是个大坏蛋
I'll always be a villain.

145
00:09:49,150 --> 00:09:51,480
噢 好啊 帅哥 要搭便车吗？
Well, hello good-looking. Need a lift?

146
00:09:51,820 --> 00:09:54,010
当然啦 你这条可爱小鱼
Certainly do, you fantastic fish, you.

147
00:09:54,190 --> 00:09:57,680
- 你快上车吧  - 我自由了！
- Get in the car, you.  - I'm free!

148
00:09:57,860 --> 00:09:59,290
是吗？
Right?

149
00:09:59,430 --> 00:10:01,420
仆人 干得好啊 送我这块表
Nice work sending me the watch, Minion.

150
00:10:01,590 --> 00:10:03,960
- 当然啦 头儿  - 冲啊！
- You got it, boss.  - Punch it!

151
00:10:05,660 --> 00:10:07,600
好 举起你们的双手
All right, put your hands in the air.

152
00:10:12,740 --> 00:10:16,140
女士们 先生们 你们的大都会侠来了！
Ladies and gentlemen, your Metro Man!

153
00:10:16,810 --> 00:10:19,510
- 谁是你们的英雄？ - 大都会侠！
- Who's your man?  - Metro Man!

154
00:10:20,050 --> 00:10:22,240
没错 大都会市市民！
Yeah, Metro City!

155
00:10:24,750 --> 00:10:26,510
来一下 来吧 来一下
Gimme some. Come on. Give it now.

156
00:10:26,690 --> 00:10:29,550
跟我来 来吧 祝福我吧 好了
Give it to me. Right on. Gimme the good stuff. All right.

157
00:10:47,940 --> 00:10:49,130
嘿 大都会市
Hey, Metro City.

158
00:10:50,540 --> 00:10:51,530
嘿 嘿
Hey. Hey.

159
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:55,970
大家现在声音小一点好吗
You know, you know, I just want to bring it down a bit.

160
00:10:56,180 --> 00:10:58,240
孩子 小点声 谢谢 伙计
Boys, a little lower. Thank you, fellas.

161
00:10:58,420 --> 00:11:00,650
我们来说点现实的
Let's get real for a moment.

162
00:11:00,850 --> 00:11:04,080
对 没错 说得对
That's right. That's right. That's right.

163
00:11:04,260 --> 00:11:07,780
虽然拥有一整个博物馆是超级棒 超级棒的事
Although getting a whole museum is super-cool, is super-cool,

